{
  "20480000": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Actually, I am planning to make a letterpress with the motif of a fighting arena, but I need a certain stone. I think I can make a more realistic letter board with the Arabiana stone, which is also used as a building material for fighting halls! The color of the Arabiana stone is very beautiful! I guess that's why the fighting arena here is so colorful. It is used as material for other buildings in this kingdom, but nowadays it is not available as it used to be, and that is a problem.": ""
  },
  "96819": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Since I saw that horrible thing in the town that night, I can't wait to drink. Even if I drink warm soup or wear a lot of clothes, it's completely useless.": ""
  },
  "96820": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Azhu and Laranja are sick. They keep saying, \"Samantha, samantha,\" and I'm worried.": ""
  },
  "96821": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Not only the bad officials of Granze Dora, but also everyone in the castle has lost their appetite. Every day there's too much food left over. What the hell is going on?": ""
  },
  "96822": {
    "<attr><feel_normal_lv1><end_attr>Oh, you know Seraphi, don't you? You've come to see her, haven't you?": ""
  },
  "96823": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv3><end_attr><shake_big>Whew!": ""
  },
  "96824": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Sorry, I've been feeling cold lately. That's right. If it's Seraphi, she's in the tenement house on the east side. I can't believe she'd set foot in that house. I can't understand what she's thinking.": ""
  },
  "96825": {
    "The Gran Zedora official in the guest room, if you are unwilling to do anything, why don't you just go back to your country?": ""
  },
  "96826": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>O God! Protect this nation from the mysterious disease that afflicts you and your people. Now...": ""
  },
  "96827": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Welcome to the house! Oh, I'm sorry. I've been feeling a little cold lately. Well...": ""
  },
  "96828": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>That's funny. Even if I don't think about the Kingdom of Gran Zedora, where the heroes live, I still get chills. Don't tell me it's because of that thing I saw that day? No! I'm sure I saw something like that by mistake. That's right. I'm sure that's right.": ""
  },
  "96829": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>It's cold and scary. Blub-blub-blub. I've been scared ever since that night.": ""
  },
  "96830": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>I have to take the place of the king of this country, who is gone, and I have to rule Alahagirolo. But now everything is so fruitless. I am so dreary now that I can hardly bring myself to do it.": ""
  },
  "96831": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>I heard that. Seraphi seems to be trying her best to save Cimmer. The people in that family are so attached to King Belmud that they're giving Seraphi a hard time, but she's really a kind girl.": ""
  },
  "96833": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Oh, my dear friend. I see you've successfully obtained the ingredients for the potion Seraphy requested. Seraphy should be waiting for you at the east tenement. Please deliver the ingredients for the potion to her as soon as possible.": ""
  },
  "97083": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Oh, I saw it! I saw it! I saw the rumored Ghost of Buffalo. And I couldn't stop the chills. So I've been dancing around like this to keep warm. Oh, it was horrible.": ""
  },
  "97084": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Seraphy is clumsy, cute, kind, and the ideal lady!": ""
  },
  "97085": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Azzoux and Laranja's illnesses have been cured, but it seems that Bad Buffalo is still roaming around this country. I don't like it. I wish someone would do something about it.": ""
  },
  "97086": {
    "Seraphy was desperate to save Chimere from the very beginning, but we didn't believe him. If I were him, I would have abandoned Chimere a long time ago. He's a big guy for such a short guy.": ""
  },
  "97087": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr>Not only the bad officials of Gran Zedora, but also everyone in the castle has regained their appetite! The diner's been very busy. Now, what shall we cook tonight?": ""
  },
  "97088": {
    "Oh, it's you. If you're looking for Seraphy, he's probably wandering around the castle. I think I saw you walking along the east wall earlier. If you want to see her, you should go there.": ""
  },
  "97089": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>O God, save your people from this mysterious disease and give your blessing to Seraphi. Save your people from this mysterious disease, and grant your blessing upon Seraphi. Now...": ""
  },
  "97090": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>I took the medicine Seraphi brought and the chills disappeared completely! She's surprisingly reliable, isn't she? Well...": ""
  },
  "97091": {
    "You knew Seraphi, didn't you? I saw her at the east wall a while ago.": ""
  },
  "97092": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Seraph gave me some medicine! After we took the medicine, both Azhu and I felt better, as if we were wearing something!": ""
  },
  "97093": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>These days, people don't like to go out at night, because the nightly encounters with Buffalo's vengeful spirits can make them sick.": ""
  },
  "97094": {
    "Serafi and you, after all the horrible things you said. What a bunch of softies you are. What? Seraphi? She said she was going to the armory in the castle. She said she wants to find out more about the grudge.": ""
  },
  "97095": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>In the middle of the night, I heard a low growl of \"Belmud\" and I went outside to find the Grudge of Buffalo. I'm pretty sure that's the same Buffalon that King Belmud tore to shreds in the first fight show! As the grudge went through my body, I got a really bad chill, and if it weren't for Seraphy and you, I'd be dead.": ""
  },
  "97096": {
    "So, Seraphy asked you to find the demon that escaped from the fighting ring. That's right. If it's the Shikabu around the courtyard, he's peddling his wares here and there, so maybe he knows something about it.": ""
  },
  "97097": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>There should be no more demons in the fighting ring, but every night, out of nowhere, a creepy voice comes out of nowhere. I get chills just thinking about it.": ""
  },
  "97098": {
    "You're looking for the demons that escaped from the fighting ring? Yes, I am. Maybe the merchants who often go out of town will know something. Ask around Shikabu, the peddler.": ""
  },
  "97099": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Hey, listen up! Buffalo's ghost is in this courtyard! He appeared right in front of me and then disappeared. I shudder just thinking about it.": ""
  },
  "97100": {
    "Seraphy asked me about the demon that escaped from the fighting ring. I don't think they're in the castle.": ""
  },
  "97101": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>I heard you're looking for the demon that was in the fighting ring. Bring him back to me for my research!": ""
  },
  "102985": {
    "「あんなに　ひどいことを　言ったのに Seraphi も　アンタも……。 まったく　とんだ　お人好したちね。": ""
  },
  "97102": {
    "Hmm? Do you know where the demons that escaped from the fighting ring are now? Well, I saw a group of demons that shouldn't live in the Al-Ahagiro region on my way back from peddling. They went into the sunshade cave, but I wonder if that might have been the ones in the fighting ring.": ""
  },
  "97103": {
    "I heard you're going to the sunken cave with Seraphi. I'll take care of him in case of emergency.": ""
  },
  "97104": {
    "Seraphy ran somewhere in a hurry just now. I think she said she was going to the sunshade cave.": ""
  },
  "97105": {
    "On my way back from peddling the other day, I saw a group of demons that shouldn't be living in the Al-Ahagiro region. They were probably demons that had escaped from the fighting grounds. They went into a sheltered cave to the south of the kingdom of Al-Ahagiro.": ""
  },
  "97106": {
    "Did I just see it wrong? Or did Seraphy really bring the demon here?": ""
  },
  "97107": {
    "You looking for Seraphy? I don't know. She's not here. You'll have to look elsewhere.": ""
  },
  "97108": {
    "<attr><feel_angry_lv1><end_attr>Hey! Seraphy brought a demon into town! What on earth is she doing?": ""
  },
  "97109": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Seraphy took the demon and ran towards the courtyard! I'm scared. Why would she bring a demon?": ""
  },
  "97110": {
    "<attr><feel_angry_lv1><end_attr>Seraphy's brought a demon out of the sunshade's cave! Oh, my God.": ""
  },
  "97111": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>How long is this grudge match gonna go on? I'm too scared to keep dancing! Somebody do something!": ""
  },
  "97112": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Buffalo is scary, and that guy with the giggle is scary, so what's going to happen to us?": ""
  },
  "97113": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Is it true that Buffalo's ghost is out there again, spreading disease? What?": ""
  },
  "97114": {
    "I suggest you and Seraphi go out of town until the noise dies down.": ""
  },
  "97115": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>The grudge I've heard so much about is finally right in front of me. I'm shaking in my knees.": ""
  },
  "97116": {
    "Seraphy is a busy girl, isn't he? This time she ran out of town as fast as she could.": ""
  },
  "97117": {
    "<attr><feel_angry_lv3><end_attr>Buffalon's ghost is coming out, Seraphy is bringing in demons, and what the hell is going on?": ""
  },
  "97118": {
    "The townspeople seem to think that if only the king were here, all this would stop, but isn't now the time for us to do something about it?": ""
  },
  "97119": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>I saw that creepy thing that appeared in the courtyard. I wonder if I'm going to get sick again.": ""
  },
  "97120": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Hey! What was that voice? It's Buffalo's grudge again, isn't it? Oh my God, I'm scared.": ""
  },
  "97121": {
    "Even though the throne is without a master, I will guard this door. No one may enter the throne room. I'm sorry, but you're going to have to turn around.": ""
  },
  "97122": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>I heard that a mysterious mage who wields the Ghost of Buffalon has appeared in the courtyard. I'm very excited!": ""
  },
  "97123": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>How can such a terrifying grudge spirit be defeated? I'm scared.": ""
  },
  "97124": {
    "<attr><feel_angry_lv3><end_attr>Hey, the demon Seraphy brought. He's one of Buffalo's ghosts, right? Seraphy... he was the source of all this.": ""
  },
  "97125": {
    "The people in town may doubt Seraphy, but we believe in him. Rest assured.": ""
  },
  "65846": {
    "The door is locked.": ""
  },
  "97194": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Whenever I'm scared or having a bad day, I just dance, dance, dance! Then I can forget about it right away.": ""
  },
  "97195": {
    "Everyone is blaming Seraphy for Buffalon's grudge and the cold spell! I wonder if it's true.": ""
  },
  "97196": {
    "Hey, you! I don't want to say it out loud, but I need you to hurry up and go to the east tenement. I'm counting on you!": ""
  },
  "97197": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Like the demons in the courtyard, I wonder if the people we've had to fight in the battle show so far are holding a grudge against King Belmud and us.": ""
  },
  "97198": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>The townspeople seem to think that if only the king were here, all this would stop, but isn't now the time for us to take action? I tried to suggest that, but no one would listen to me. Huh.": ""
  },
  "97199": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Seraphy is the one who gave me the pills. She can't be one of the bad guys. But they don't believe me.": ""
  },
  "97200": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>It was a good and peaceful country when King Belmud was here. I miss those days so much.": ""
  },
  "97201": {
    "<attr><feel_angry_lv1><end_attr>Seraphy doesn't seem to be hanging around town these days. I think he's suspicious after all.": ""
  },
  "83222": {
    "扉には　カギが　かかっている。": ""
  },
  "97202": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Good, you found Seraphy. Leave her to us. You can go in peace.": ""
  },
  "97203": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr>Welcome back! I've been waiting for you. Seraphy is in the east tenement, so hurry up and go.": ""
  },
  "97204": {
    "<attr><feel_angry_lv1><end_attr>Seraphy and you, the stranger, are doing so well, but the people in the town are not.": ""
  },
  "97205": {
    "So you're finally going to work with Seraphy to exterminate the Grudge. I'm praying for your victory!": ""
  },
  "97206": {
    "<attr><feel_angry_lv1><end_attr>I just saw Seraphy heading for the fighting ring. What's he going to do now?": ""
  },
  "97207": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Everyone in town wants to demonize someone because of the fear of the grudge and the uncertainty of not having a king. But I'm sure they'll believe Seraphi when the grudge is gone.": ""
  },
  "97208": {
    "Seraphy is headed to the fighting hall of the fighting arena to draw a magic circle. The rest is up to you. Good luck!": ""
  },
  "99879": {
    "扉には　カギが　かかっている。": ""
  },
  "97209": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr>♪ Run, run, run, run ♪ I give this dance to our new leader, Seraphi! I hope you'll sit back, relax and enjoy the show.": ""
  },
  "97210": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Seraphy is the leader of this country and the heart and soul of our three brothers! That's what we decided.": ""
  },
  "97211": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr>I guess we are better judges of people than the adults who doubted Seraphi!": ""
  },
  "97212": {
    "In order to protect Al-Ahagiro, people take on the form of demons, and demons take on the form of people. Maybe we're one of them?": ""
  },
  "97213": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>I have to make a lot of delicious food for our new leader, Seraphi, and feed her!": ""
  },
  "97214": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>As you know, this is not a castle, but a monster fighting ring. If you're here to see Seraphy, head to the throne room on the third floor of the castle.": ""
  },
  "97215": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr>The grudge trouble has subsided, but now it's time for Al-Ahagiro to make a name for itself. Seraphy and I will work together and do our best.": ""
  },
  "97216": {
    "The official from Gran Zedora. He's writing a letter to the state saying that Seraphy is now in charge of the country.": ""
  },
  "97217": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Seraphi is a wonderful daughter. That's why we must not rely too much on her. Now, let's see...": ""
  },
  "97218": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>If you lost the past, you can make the future. I agree wholeheartedly. Well...": ""
  },
  "97219": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr>I heard that you defeated a demon's vengeance spirit that appeared in the fighting arena. Everyone is thanking you from the bottom of their hearts!": ""
  },
  "97220": {
    "Seeing Seraphy in the throne room, I finally realized that King Belmud is really gone.": ""
  },
  "97221": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>When I grow up, I'm going to be a smart and kind woman like Seraphi!": ""
  },
  "97222": {
    "King Belmud is still the only king of our kingdom. But Seraphi is an important companion who will lead our country together.": ""
  },
  "97223": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>It doesn't mean that I don't miss the days of King Belmud, but we can't just keep looking back to the past. We must make the future of Al-Ahagiro with the hands of everyone in this country now. That's what I've finally come to believe.": ""
  },
  "97224": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>The throne room is open to all citizens and travelers. Now, feel free to enter.": ""
  },
  "97225": {
    "With new leadership, this country is quickly coming back to life. I wish our Granzedola could be like that.": ""
  },
  "97226": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>After all, it's a shame we couldn't get a sample of the Buffalo Ghost or the mage or whatever he's called.": ""
  },
  "97227": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Simele ran around town convincing everyone that Seraphi wasn't a bad girl, that she was a good girl.": ""
  },
  "97228": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr>Ah!<pc> Mr.! I'm so glad you came! I wanted to thank you. I couldn't have saved everyone in Al-Ahagiro and Mr. Gorius by myself. Thank you so, so, so much for saving Al-Ahagiro! I'd be lying if I said I didn't want to go back to my old world, but everyone in this town needs me. We all have to protect Al-Ahagiro for Mr. Belmud and Mr. Gorius from now on. Together with the people of this town who have lost their memories of the past, we will create a new future for me in this world. I will make this country, which has seen too much sadness, a happy country full of smiles, so watch over the future of Al-Ahagiro!": ""
  },
  "97229": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr><pc> I'm so, so, so grateful that Al-Ahagiro was there to save my life. Thank you, thank you, thank you! We will protect Al-Ahagiro for Mr. Belmud and Mr. Gorius, and for all of us. Someday I will make Al-Ahagiro a happy country full of smiling faces, so please watch over the future of this country!": ""
  },
  "97230": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>Looking back calmly, Seraphy had always done everything for this country. I can't believe I ever doubted her. I'm ashamed of myself.": ""
  },
  "97231": {
    "The Buffalo Ghosts that haunted them, the demons that escaped from the fighting ring, they turned human before they disappeared. Something strange must have happened, but somehow it didn't surprise me. It was as if I had always known.": ""
  },
  "99881": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr>「西の城壁から　モンスター格闘場の 王族専用観覧席へと通じる　扉のカギを Seraphi が　解放したぞ。 「この国には　もう　王も　臣下もないのだから みんなが　自由に通れるように　とのことだ。 お前も　行ってみるといいだろう。": ""
  },
  "82540": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv3><end_attr>Meat Niku Nigu Niguー！！ After all, meat dishes are the best! No matter how many times I eat it, I'll never get tired of it!<bw_break>": ""
  },
  "82541": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>But, you know, everyone else seems to be fed up with a life of eating only meat. It's a luxury for such a delicious food.<bw_break>": ""
  },
  "82542": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Yes, that's right! I remembered a dish I saw in a picture book that looked delicious. What was it called? I think it was a dish called \"sasandrovich\", where the meat is placed between bread or something like that. It was a dish called \"sasandrovich,\" which is meat between bread or something like that. If that sandorovich is good, I want everyone to eat it. Well, now that we've decided that, let's make the best of it! I'm sorry, but could you bring me some bread or something from somewhere? I need bread that goes well with Sandorovich.": ""
  },
  "82543": {
    "<attr><feel_normal_lv1><end_attr>Oh, you'll take care of it! I'm in your debt! I'm sure I'll repay you for this, so bring me some good bread, will you? I just wonder where I can find such a thing? I don't know, but if we go to a place where bread is famous, we might be able to get some good bread.": ""
  },
  "82544": {
    "<attr><feel_normal_lv1><end_attr>Oh, you'll take care of it! I'm in your debt! But you look like you've got a lot of work to do. I'll take care of my business later, so come back when you can spare a little more time.": ""
  },
  "82545": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>I see. It's a pity, because I thought everyone would be pleased if I could make Sandorovich. I wish I could have had it.": ""
  },
  "82546": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Those of you who have had enough of meat will be reminded of the wonders of meat when you try sandorovich. Bring me some bread to go with the sandorovich.<open_irai><bw_break>": ""
  },
  "82547": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>I only know about the desert area, so I don't know much about it, but if you go to a place where bread is famous, you might be able to get some good bread.": ""
  },
  "82548": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Hey, you. How's it going? Did you find the right bread for Sandorovich?<open_irai><bw_break>": ""
  },
  "82549": {
    "<attr><feel_normal_lv1><end_attr>What? You mean to tell me that your grandmother, who can make bread to go with sandorovich, told you to bring a bronze knife with at least two stars? I see. You can't make Sandorovich without using a carefully selected knife, huh? Well, now that I know what's going on, I'll ask you to hurry up.": ""
  },
  "82550": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Did you find the right bread for Sandorovich? I'll wait for you here, so bring me some quickly. I'm counting on you.": ""
  },
  "82551": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv2><end_attr>You didn't get it yet? Too bad. I'm getting an itch to try Sandorovich's.": ""
  },
  "82552": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv2><end_attr>Oh, this is the perfect bread for Sandorovich. Let's see. Wow. It's soft and has a nice texture. Well then, let's put my favorite meat between this bread and complete the Sandorovich. I'm looking forward to it.": ""
  },
  "82553": {
    "Wow! This is amazing! When you bite into it, the juices soak into the bread, giving it a taste unlike anything you've ever tasted before!": ""
  },
  "82554": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv3><end_attr>It's all thanks to you that I was able to find such good food! I thank you! Please accept this as a thank you!": ""
  },
  "82555": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>I'm sure those of you who have had enough of meat will be more than happy to chow down on this Sandorovich! This is a meat revolution that will change the desert diet!": ""
  },
  "82556": {
    "Would you give Lerg a piece of Kope's fluffy bread?<yesno><case 1><break><case 2><close><case_cancel><close>": ""
  },
  "82557": {
    "<pc> gave Lerg a loaf of Kope fluffy bread!": ""
  },
  "82558": {
    "Ragh, who had just finished making sandwiches, began to eat them enthusiastically.": ""
  },
  "82559": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>I'm sure those of you who have had enough of meat will be more than happy to chow down on this Sandorovich! This is a meat revolution that will change the desert diet!": ""
  },
  "82565": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Ever since King Belmud passed away, something has changed in this town. Everyone is on edge. The loss of the battle show is a big factor. Everyone was looking forward to it. Ah~ ah. I wonder if there is an interesting game that can relieve everyone's stress. Something that lots of people can participate in, that doesn't cost a lot of money, and is easy to do. Hey, you. You're traveling around, aren't you? Can you find some interesting games for us?": ""
  },
  "82566": {
    "<attr><feel_happy_lv1><end_attr>Oh, you'll do it? Thank you very much! I'll be sure to return the favor! Well, I heard a rumor on the wind that somewhere in this world, there's a man named Saudi who knows every kind of game and is the best at it. I don't know where he is, but maybe he's in a place where people like to have fun. Maybe we can find some fun games to play with him.": ""
  },
  "82567": {
    "<attr><feel_normal_lv1><end_attr>Oh, you'll do it? That's great! But, you seem to have a lot of work to do. You can take care of my business later, so come back when you can spare a little more time.": ""
  },
  "82568": {
    "<attr><feel_sad_lv1><end_attr>Seriously. What are we supposed to look forward to from now on? Ah~ ah. This is so boring.": ""
  },
  "82569": {
